        "body": "<p>Anne Klein is committed to empowering women who wear its brand by partnering with entrepreneurial women to develop a print capsule collection that connects with our consumers. Our commitment to diversity and the arts provides a platform to engage and enhance visibility.</p><p>Our mission is to spotlight entrepreneurial women in the arts, offering a platform for their creativity and empowering talented female print designers. This series is more than just a showcase of beautiful designs, it is a celebration of storytelling and representation. Each piece reflects the experiences, passions, and vision of the artist behind it.</p><p>We are proud to bring these voices to the forefront through the Anne Klein Artist Series Collection.</p>"
